{"lemma":"طَوْرَيْ","slug":"طَوْرَيْ","root":"ط.#.ر","root_slug":"ط-_-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-_-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"طَوْر","root":"طور","pos":"N","occurrence_count":10},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27278"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of طَارَ (ṭāra) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","uncountable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"time, stage, phase, stadium","examples":[{"text":"وَأَشَارَ إِلَى أَنَّهُ “مُذْ أَقْفَلَ ٱلْمَعْبَرَ وَأُقْفِلَتْ مَعَهُ ٱلْمَعَابِرُ ٱلشَّرْقِيَّةُ لِسُورِيَا ٱلْمُوصِلَةُ إِلَى ٱلدَّاخِلِ ٱلْعَرَبِيِّ، أُعْطِبَتْ ذَهَابًا وَإِيَابًا حَرَكَةُ ٱلتَّبَادُلِ ٱلتِّجَارِيِّ ٱلَّتِي سَنَكُونُ ٱلْآنَ فِي طَوْرِ إِعَادَةِ إِحْيَائِهَا مِنَ ٱلْأَرَاضِي ٱللُّبْنَانِيَّةِ إِلَى ٱلدَّاخِلِ ٱلسُّورِيِّ، وَمِنْهُ إِلَى ٱلدَّاخِلِ ٱلْأُرْدُنِيِّ مِنْ خِلَالِ ٱلْمَعْبَرِ ٱلْمُسْتَعَادِ إِلَى ٱلدَّوْلَةِ ٱلسُّورِيَّةِ، لِلْاِنْتِقَالِ إِلَى ٱلْعِرَاقِ وَدُوَلِ ٱلْخَلِيجِ (ٱلْفَارِسِيِّ)”."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mode","examples":[{"text":"طَوْر الْقِصَّة","english":"campaign/story mode"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to further, to bring forward, to develop"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mountain","tags":["Classical"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Aramaic טוּרָא / ܛܘܪܐ (ṭūrā, “mountain, high territory”). Ultimately from Proto-West Semitic *ṯ̣ūr-. Doublet of ظِرّ (ẓirr) and زُرَر (zurar, “flint”)."},"ipa":["/tˤawr/","/tˤaw.wa.ra/","/tˤuːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27278","headword_ar":"طَورِىٌّ","root":"Twr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wild; that estranges himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"itself, from mankind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, K;) applied to a bird, (S, O,) and to a man; (S, A, O;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuwraAniY~N","text_ar":"طُورَانِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAmN TuwriY~N","text_ar":"حَمَامٌ طُورِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuwraAniY~N","text_ar":"طُورَانِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wild pigeons:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) so called in relation to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~uwru","text_ar":"الطُّورُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a certain mountain; or the mountain is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tur~aAn","text_ar":"طُرَّان"},{"kind":"text","text":", and [if so] it is an irreg. rel. n.: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that have come from a distant country."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuzofN","text_ar":"عُزْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEaAriybu Tuwriy~uwna","text_ar":"اَعَارِيبُ طُورِيُّونَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wild Arabs of the desert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"that avoid the towns and villages, from fear of epidemic disease, and of perdition: as though they were thus called in relation to the mountain named"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~uwr","text_ar":"الطُّور"},{"kind":"text","text":", in Syria. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN TuwriY~N","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ طُورِىٌّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stranger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA bihaA","text_ar":"مَا بِهَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuwriY~N","text_ar":"طُورِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, O, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuwraAniY~N","text_ar":"طُورَانِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAld~aAri","text_ar":"بِالدَّارِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"A, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, A, O, K:) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwriY~N","text_ar":"دُورِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","TA","A","K","Lth"]}]}}